$ cd /usr/local/
$ sudo wget http://nginx.org/download/nginx-1.8.0.tar.gz
$ sudo tar -zxvf nginx-1.8.0.tar.gz
$ cd nginx-1.8.0
--with-http_ssl_module --with-pcre    ssl模块
$ sudo ./configure --prefix=/usr/local/nginx --with-http_ssl_module --with-pcre  #这一步需要按需要添加编译参数，如下
$ sudo make
$ sudo make install




重新编译nginx添加 ssl模块

https://blog.csdn.net/u012946310/article/details/85106653